  "texts": [
    "We then used these pre-trained embeddings to create a predictive model for each disease.",
    "In line with the majority of other similar studies (Si et al., 2021), a Bidirectional GRU was chosen for the prediction head.",
    "We also added a global max pooling layer and a sigmoid output.",
    "We evaluated both frozen and finetuned embeddings and compared the performance to a model trained from randomly-initialized embeddings.",
    "The Keras library was used for modeling."
  ],
